<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to <%= companyName %>
  </title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../view/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div style="padding: 20px;"></div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="logo" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="<%= companyName %> Logo" width="150">
      </div>

      <h1 style="color: #333333; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome to <%= companyName %>!</h1>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello <%= userName %>,</p>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">Thank you for signing up with
        <%= companyName %>. We're excited to have you on board! Your account has been successfully created and is ready
          to use.</p>

      <h2 style="color: #333333; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Your API Key</h2>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">Below is your API key that
        you'll need for making requests to our services:</p>

      <div class="code-container"
        style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">
        <%= apiKey %>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: #fff4e5; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 3px;">
        <p style="color: #e65100; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">⚠️ Important:</p>
        <p style="color: #663c00; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Please store this API key safely. If you lose it, you
          will need to reset it, which will invalidate your previous key and require updating any integrations. We
          cannot recover this key for you once it's stored in our system.</p>
      </div>

      <h3 style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">How to Use Your API Key</h3>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px;">Include your API key in the
        header of your HTTP requests:</p>

      <div
        style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        X-API-Key: <%= apiKey %>
      </div>

      <h3 style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Getting Started</h3>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">Visit our <a
          href="<%= apiDocsUrl %>" style="color: #4285f4; text-decoration: none;">API documentation</a> to learn how to
        make your first API call and explore all available endpoints.</p>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">If you have any questions or
        need assistance, don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

      <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome aboard!<br>The <%=
          companyName %> Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %>
          <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <%= companyAddress %><br>
          <a href="<%= privacyUrl %>" style="color: #999999;">Privacy Policy</a> |
          <a href="<%= termsUrl %>" style="color: #999999;">Terms of Service</a> |
          <a href="<%= supportUrl %>" style="color: #999999;">Contact Support</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>